{"tid":1572910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其 實 大 家 係 咪 唔 識 爬 文 ？","createTime":"2019-09-15T20:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T05:09:09.000Z","uid":431,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8449cf177b652177d79cef4d4c87fc17d41ea030","tid":1572910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:19:55.000Z","msg":"請大家唔好再屌柒雙花巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572804</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雙花ching真係手足嚟 爬晒文就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有班人屌唔切屈人係狗做乜柒？<br />\n<br />\n唔止依單嘢 好多post明明睇多一兩頁就唔會炒車<br />\n但班盲撚永遠睇頭幾個comment就跟住屌咗先<br />\n無嘢下嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係懶到要食殘廢餐都撳下睇下有無圖睇先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爬文都唔識學咩人上連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843d589a22f95858d50599a01a723c32db49e03f","tid":1572910,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9891aef0998906c756c3091ed47b35c925deaaaf","tid":1572910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:21:16.000Z","msg":"繼續留言屈狗屌手足嗰班人你哋做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc4e8f2d6ebb3b12212fbb84870829ef61e4eb0","tid":1572910,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"843d589a22f95858d50599a01a723c32db49e03f","tid":1572910,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e050e7254cc9a475a71539596ff7d15184e0fe19","tid":1572910,"uid":130140,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:40:08.000Z","msg":"而家好多人求鳩其睇完就放低個推字就算，其實你無意見可以出返去就得，尊重下出post嘅巴絲打得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n被捕手足個po講撚左唔好再推，再推害死人